WEBVTT

00:04.101 --> 00:05.252
Today is Sankranti.

00:08.002 --> 00:14.802
Sankranti means something
new is happening today.

00:21.352 --> 00:25.752
Kundalini awakened inside you.

00:27.653 --> 00:31.552
And you are become new.

00:33.302 --> 00:37.802
But now on the day of
Sankranti you should know

00:40.102 --> 00:45.752
That the Goddess sitting inside you

00:46.702 --> 00:49.952
Has to pleased.

00:53.902 --> 00:58.702
What should we do to make her happy?

01:03.752 --> 01:05.252
Gave sesame and jaggery.

01:07.801 --> 01:09.803
This is for love.

01:11.204 --> 01:17.052
To increase mutual love.
Sesame and jaggery are given.

01:18.502 --> 01:22.152
And today the sun left

01:23.502 --> 01:26.503
its place and came to us in Uttarayan.

01:29.052 --> 01:32.452
At this moment we

01:34.603 --> 01:38.702
should thank him very much!

01:41.401 --> 01:47.402
Because of his grace lots of
things happening in our country.

01:50.458 --> 01:54.802
You all should greet the sun.

01:59.652 --> 02:06.402
And his power, his knowledge
and light should come in us.

02:14.602 --> 02:19.102
I would say that,all of you have awakened.

02:20.902 --> 02:23.302
Consciousness is flowing in you.

02:25.402 --> 02:32.152
Now use this enlightenment.
bring strength in you

02:33.751 --> 02:36.252
and bring peace in you.

02:37.402 --> 02:42.102
And tell the world that
there is this power in yourself.

02:43.582 --> 02:45.582
And we have to get it.

02:47.982 --> 02:52.392
Find it by

02:54.202 --> 03:00.702
Your virtues and by
your truths, increase it.

03:03.152 --> 03:05.052
Today is a special day.

03:06.952 --> 03:12.102
The reason is that Sun has
special favor is on us today.

03:17.952 --> 03:21.902
We should thanks to him.

03:23.802 --> 03:31.152
You have got a lot and you will get more.

03:31.152 --> 03:33.352
It should be increased.

03:34.002 --> 03:36.752
You have worshiped me so much.

03:37.102 --> 03:40.152
I am shocked,

03:41.502 --> 03:46.402
What do you want by worshiping me?

03:51.752 --> 03:56.004
I want you to become very Big Sahajyogi

03:57.252 --> 03:59.252
And there must be a thousands of people.

04:00.402 --> 04:05.652
Bring this world on virtuous
path. Teach goodness.

04:07.152 --> 04:14.353
And feel the power
that is flowing inside you.

04:17.282 --> 04:21.632
I am very happy to see you all.
